M/S. General Sales Pvt. Ltd. vs Gopal Mukherjee, Income Tax ... on 20 February, 1987Equivalent citations: 1987 166 ITR 87 SC, 1987 Supp (1) SCC 737
Bench: M M Dutt, R Pathak, R Mishra
ORDER
  

